ice storm! Chirag and I looked over your draft of the magazine article and
we both loved it. I am forwarding the original along with a few of our
edits to our advisors, Drs. Haberman and Hamilton, for review. Thank you
again so much for interviewing us and I will follow up soon!

Best,
Lizette Wong

